description: Mega Uranium Ltd., a mineral exploration and development company, explores for uranium prospective properties primarily in Australia and Canada. The company hold interest in the Ben Lomond property comprising of 2 mining leases covering an area of 21.6 square kilometers located in Queensland, Australia. It also holds interest in Georgetown (Maureen) projects located in Queensland, Australia; and Redport project located in Western Australia. The company was formerly known as Maple Minerals Corp. and changed its name to Mega Uranium Ltd. in October 2005. Mega Uranium Ltd. was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Richard J. Patricio L.L.B., LL.B.
